title: Wolf Pack football: Nevada, New Mexico underway
text:
Wolf Pack football: Nevada, New Mexico underway Staff report 4:31 p.m. PDT October 10, 2015 Nevadaâ€™s Lenny Jones celebrates a stop last week against UNLV. (Photo: Jason Bean/RGJ) CONNECT 2 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
The Nevada and New Mexico football teams have kicked off at Mackay Stadium in Reno. 
The Mountain West game between the Wolf Pack (2-3, 0-1 MW) and Lobos (3-2, 1-0) comes a week after Nevada lost to rival UNLV at home. The Wolf Pack has lost three of its last four games overall. 
RGJ Wolf Pack beat writer Chris Murray is at Mackay Stadium covering the action; follow him at @MurrayRGJ or see his live Twitter stream below. Updates will also be available at RGJ.com . Read or Share this story: http://on.rgj.com/1LoqwMf TOP VIDEOS
